net.krotscheck.dfr

Class FileStreamDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.krotscheck.dfr.FileStreamDecoder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<Map<String,Object>>, IFilteringDataStream

    public final class FileStreamDecoder
extends Object
implements IFilteringDataStream, Iterable<Map<String,Object>>, Closeable
    This class provides a convenience class by which files may be quickly decoded. It uses the Java ServiceLoader to discover all appropriate implementations of IDataDecoder, and creates one based on your passed mimetype.
    Author:
    Michael Krotscheck
